Package: scraping-service
Version: 1.0.0-1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Mohammed Al-Zubiri
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-venv
Description: Books scraping pipeline and FastAPI service
 Scrapes data from books.toscrape.com, cleans and stores records in SQLite,
 and exposes query endpoints via FastAPI. Includes systemd service integration.
